imdb.plot outline: WeHo Politics is a limited web series that followed a talk show format where Max Geschwind played the host/reporter interviewing candidates running for City Council in the wonderful city of West Hollywood, California talking about issues such as social justice, affordable housing, parking, traffic, development and city corruption.
